01:03:02,695 --> 01:03:04,572
She gives me courage.

791
01:03:07,950 --> 01:03:09,285
What a great friend.

792
01:03:10,244 --> 01:03:11,245
You're right.

793
01:03:12,038 --> 01:03:14,791
You should never run away.
It's not a good thing to do.

794
01:03:16,667 --> 01:03:17,794
But you see, Jun-u,

795
01:03:19,587 --> 01:03:21,839
I ran away like a coward.

796
01:03:24,759 --> 01:03:27,887
No, you came back like this.

797
01:03:33,309 --> 01:03:35,228
I came here to ask you for a favor.

798
01:03:39,482 --> 01:03:41,442
Don't visit me like that again.

799
01:03:49,450 --> 01:03:51,661
CHOE MYEONG-JUN

800
01:03:52,078 --> 01:03:54,205
Thank goodness I saw this letter first.

801
01:03:55,790 --> 01:03:57,625
It's all in the past, you know.

802
01:03:58,042 --> 01:03:59,544
You're all grown up now,

803
01:03:59,877 --> 01:04:01,254
and I have another family.

804
01:04:02,338 --> 01:04:04,632
I think we each have

805
01:04:05,883 --> 01:04:08,177
different paths to take.

806
01:04:09,595 --> 01:04:11,055
Do you understand?

807
01:04:14,851 --> 01:04:16,143
I'm sorry, Jun-u.

808
01:04:50,428 --> 01:04:52,722
Could you please drive a little faster?

809
01:05:48,903 --> 01:05:49,904
Jun-u!

810
01:05:54,700 --> 01:05:56,160
Jun-u, are you all right?

811
01:05:59,747 --> 01:06:00,748
Soo-bin.

812
01:06:48,337 --> 01:06:51,507
My mom still thinks that the time
she spent with her first love

813
01:06:51,590 --> 01:06:54,343
years ago was the most
beautiful moment in her life.

814
01:06:54,760 --> 01:06:56,095
Back when she was 18.

815
01:06:56,178 --> 01:06:59,265
Writing a letter like this
is the only thing I can do now,

816
01:06:59,348 --> 01:07:02,018
but I'm here for you. Let's stay strong.

817
01:07:02,101 --> 01:07:03,894
I miss you, and I like you.

818
01:07:03,978 --> 01:07:06,522
-Can't you take care of it again?
-How dare you!

819
01:07:06,814 --> 01:07:08,899
It turned out to be me. The informant.

820
01:07:08,983 --> 01:07:11,402
Drawing, art, and art school.

821
01:07:11,485 --> 01:07:12,486
Soo-bin.

822
01:07:13,821 --> 01:07:15,197
I have a goal now.

823
01:07:15,364 --> 01:07:18,034
Big news. People from the Office
of the Education came to get Hwi-yeong.

824
01:07:18,117 --> 01:07:19,285
I admit all the allegations.

825
01:07:19,368 --> 01:07:20,828
I'll cooperate with the investigation.

826
01:07:20,911 --> 01:07:22,079
Happy birthday.

827
01:07:25,082 --> 01:07:27,168
Let's go now. I'll walk you home.

828
01:07:40,056 --> 01:07:42,475
Subtitle translation by Wayne Ryu

